The evidence with the title 'The Good Girl - Wikipedia ' says The Good Girl is a 2002 American black comedy-drama film directed by Miguel Arteta from a script by Mike White, and stars Jennifer Aniston, Jake Gyllenhaal and John C. Reilly .  ... . From Jennifer Aniston and Jake Gyllenhaal, the Good Girl is a moving and astute look at the passions of two troubled souls in a small town . " .
